{"title":"Paper. Neutropenia febril-2025","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/Paper. Neutropenia febril-2025.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"MANEJO DE LA\\NNEUTROPENIA FEBRIL","guid":"-HH8MmvC0ceMQgYkllYOyw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"## INTRODUCCIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- Intensificación de esquemas de\\Nquimioterapia en neoplasias hematológicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"- Mejoría notable\\Nen pronóstico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"- Toxicidad importante →\\Nmorbimortalidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"- Mielosupresión severa y\\Nprolongada requiere","guid":"","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"- Medidas de aislamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"- Apoyo transfusional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"- Profilaxis\\Nantimicrobianas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"5","text":"- Tratamiento antibiótico\\Noportuno y eficaz","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"- Riesgo de\\Ninfección depende\\Nde","guid":"","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"- Profundidad y\\Nduración de\\Nneutropenia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"- Presencia de mucositis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"- Comorbilidades\\Ndel paciente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"1","text":"- Neutropenia y deterioro\\Ninmunidad innata","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"- Pérdida de fagocitosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"- Eliminación\\Nbacteriana\\Ncomprometida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"- Respuesta\\Ninflamatoria\\Nalterada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"- Activación inmunidad celular y\\Nhumoral comprometidas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"14","text":"- Cuadros sépticos con letalidad\\N>90% sin manejo adecuado","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"## INFECCIONES\\NFRECUENTES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"- Orales: periodontales, partes\\Nblandas (gingivales), faríngeas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"- Perianales: hemorroides\\Ncomplicados, fisuras","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"- Colónicas: tiflitis asociadas\\Na mucositis intensas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"20","text":"- Piel: flebitis, acné,\\Npústulas (foliculitis)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"## AGENTES\\NINFECCIOSOS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"- Bacterias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"- Antes: bacilos G(-) entéricos (E.\\NColi, Klebsiella, Proteus)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"- Últimos 15 años: G(+) como\\Nstaphilococo y estreptococo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"- Sensibilidad antibiótica\\Nvaría según centro","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"25","text":"- Hongos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"- No suele ser\\Ninfección primaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"- Asociada a uso prolongado de\\Nantibióticos, catéteres, disrupción\\Nmucosa, esteroides","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"- Cándida: patógeno\\Nmás frecuente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"30","text":"- Aspergillus: segundo\\Nmás frecuente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"30","text":"- Con profilaxis antimicótica\\N(fluconazol): problema principal\\Nson hongos filamentosos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"30","text":"- En LLA/patología linfoide con esteroides:\\Nriesgo de Pneumocistis jiroveci","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"30","text":"- En inmunosupresión celular:\\Nriesgo de Micobacterium TBC","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"25","text":"- Virus","guid":"","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"- Más frecuentes: Virus Herpes\\NSimple I y II (oral y genital)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"- Menos frecuente:\\NHerpes Zoster (cutáneo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"- Otros virus en pacientes con trasplante de\\Nprogenitores hematopoyéticos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"38","text":"- Aciclovir recomendado para\\Nlesiones mucosas o genitales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"38","text":"- Virus respiratorios requieren\\Nprevención, profilaxis,\\Ndiagnóstico y terapia oportuna","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"25","text":"- Micobacterium TBC","guid":"","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"- No es problema habitual\\Ndurante neutropenia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"- Sin recomendación\\Nestandarizada de profilaxis","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"0","text":"## ORGANIZACIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"- Desarrollo: Programa Nacional de\\NCáncer del Adulto (PANDA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"- Origen: evaluación 1998 de\\Nleucemia aguda a nivel nacional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"- Mortalidad precoz en primer mes:\\N23% (rango 80%-20%)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"47","text":"- Taller de infectólogos y\\Nhematólogos de centros PANDA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"47","text":"- Objetivo: mantener mortalidad\\Nrelacionada a quimioterapia <10%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"47","text":"- Considera sólo neutropenia\\Nfebril de alto riesgo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"47","text":"- Resultados 2011: mortalidad <5% en\\Ntodos los centros acreditados","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"0","text":"## DEFINICIONES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"- Neutropenia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"- Recuento absoluto de\\Nneutrófilos (RAN) <1000 x mm³","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"- Neutropenia leve: RAN\\N1000-500 x mm³","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"- Neutropenia moderada:\\NRAN 499-100 x mm³","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"56","text":"- Neutropenia severa:\\NRAN <100 x mm³","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"55","text":"- Neutropenia febril","guid":"","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"- Temperatura oral >37,5°C en\\Npaciente con RAN <500 x mm³","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"- Paciente afebril con foco\\Nclínico y RAN <500 x mm³","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"- Paciente febril, afebril o con\\Nhipotermia en contexto de shock\\Nséptico y RAN <500 x mm³","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"55","text":"- Neutropenia febril\\Nde alto riesgo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"- Diagnóstico reciente de neoplasia con\\Ninfiltración extensa medular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"- Inicio de quimioterapia con\\NRAN <1000 x mm³","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"- Neutropenia de instalación rápida (día\\N8°-10° post quimioterapia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"65","text":"- RAN <100 x mm³","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"65","text":"- Duración\\Nproyectada >7\\Ndías","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"65","text":"- Asociada a\\Nmucositis intensa","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"55","text":"- Factores de riesgo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"- Edad >60 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"- Comorbilidades","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"- Temperatura oral >39°C","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"- Parámetros SIRS: taquicardia,\\Ntaquipnea, fiebre/hipotermia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"72","text":"- Parámetros de\\Nshock séptico","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"0","text":"## TRATAMIENTO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"- Emergencia médica (100% mortalidad\\Nsin tratamiento adecuado)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"- Hospitalización","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"- Idealmente en Unidad de\\NAislamiento protector simple","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"- Riesgo vital por infección y necesidad de\\Nmedidas terapéuticas precoces","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"78","text":"- Anamnesis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"- Definir día de\\Nquimioterapia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"- Aplasia medular entre día\\N9º-10º hasta 20º-23º","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"- Evaluar síntomas en sitios con alta\\Nconcentración de flora comensal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"78","text":"- Examen físico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"- Estado general y\\Nhemodinamia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"- Cavidad oral: mucositis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"- Pulmonar:\\Ncrépitos,\\Nasimetrías","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"87","text":"- Abdominal:\\Ndolor, blumberg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"87","text":"- Región perianal:\\Nhemorroides, fisuras, dolor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"87","text":"- Piel: flebitis, infección relacionada a\\Ncatéter, celulitis, foliculitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"87","text":"- Evitar\\Nprocedimientos\\Ninvasivos","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"0","text":"## EXÁMENES DE\\NLABORATORIO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"- Hemocultivos corrientes (dos de\\Nambas extremidades superiores)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"- Urocultivo con\\Nantibiograma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"- Hemograma con\\Nrecuento plaquetario","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"95","text":"- Pruebas hepáticas, glicemia, uricemia,\\Ncreatininemia, electrolitos, LDH","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"95","text":"- PT y TTPK si sospecha\\Ndiscrasia sanguínea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"95","text":"- Clasificación\\Ngrupo sanguíneo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"0","text":"## INDICACIONES\\NGENERALES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"- Reducción exposición\\Nflora intrahospitalaria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"- Higiene de\\Nmanos rigurosa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"- Mascarilla N95 (reduce\\Nesporas de hongos y\\Ntransmisión\\Nviral/micobacterias)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"102","text":"- Alimentación: régimen cocido,\\Nlíquidos abundantes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"102","text":"- Procedimientos invasivos:\\Nretirar y reinstalar vías venosas\\Ncon técnica aséptica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"102","text":"- Reducción\\Nflora comensal","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"- Ducha diaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"- Enjuagues bucales\\Nantisépticos cada 6h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"- Tránsito intestinal diario","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"102","text":"- Preservar indemnidad de\\Nbarreras cutáneo-mucosas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"- Evitar\\Nprocedimientos\\Ninvasivos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"- No enemas/terapias IM con\\Nplaquetas <20.000 x mm³","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"- Técnica aséptica en\\Naccesos venosos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"- Aseo diario de sitios de\\Ninserción y lesiones cutáneas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"102","text":"- Hidratación: suero fisiológico\\N3000 cc/24h + 2g KCl/l","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"102","text":"- Apoyo transfusional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"- 6U plaquetas si\\Nrecuento <10.000 x mm³","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"- 2U glóbulos\\Nrojos si Hb <8 g/l","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"0","text":"## TRATAMIENTO\\NANTIBIÓTICO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"- Conceptos generales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"- Precocidad (<2h\\Nde diagnóstico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"- Empírico (no\\Nesperar cultivos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"- Cobertura contra bacterias\\Ngram negativas entéricas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"122","text":"- Bactericida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"122","text":"- Asociado a\\Naminoglucósidos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"122","text":"- Dosis de carga y\\Nfraccionadas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"122","text":"- Dosis altas vía\\Nendovenosa","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"0","text":"## PROTOCOLOS\\NANTIBIÓTICOS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"- 1ª línea:\\NCeftriaxona-Amikacina","guid":"","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"- NFAR sin compromiso hemodinámico\\Nsin foco o con foco pulmonar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"- NFAR sin compromiso hemodinámico con\\Nfoco abdominal/perianal (+Metronidazol)","guid":"tw4OiELL9X2no6v92myjgw","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"- NFAR sin compromiso hemodinámico con\\Nfoco cutáneo (+Cefazolina/Vancomicina)","guid":"DxFKbMkvjGVt_W5UKxcIcg","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"130","text":"- 2ª línea:\\NTazobactam-Amikacina","guid":"","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"- Pacientes sin\\Nrespuesta a 1ª línea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"- Antecedente de hospitalización prolongada","guid":"se40Zz0CLUnT-MvwT0JlLw","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"- Episodio previo con agente resistente a Ceftriaxona","guid":"PDOaiO0DbhhTG_qSMF6A_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"130","text":"- 3ª línea:\\NImipenem-Amikacina","guid":"","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"- NFAR con compromiso hemodinámico con/sin foco","guid":"RAvnzlRa6quDfPsb9CfkDw","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"- En mucositis extensa o sepsis relacionada a catéter: agregar Vancomicina","guid":"yIpsgbmlkv6VW5KjVj3rvA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"0","text":"## EVALUACIÓN DEL\\NTRATAMIENTO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"- A las 48h: parámetros clínicos y\\Nresultados de cultivos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"- A las 72h: según evolución mantener\\Nesquema o ampliar cobertura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"142","text":"- A los 5-7 días: reevaluación\\Ncompleta, considerar\\NAnfotericina si persiste fiebre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"142","text":"- Paciente afebril: suspender antibióticos\\Nsegún criterios específicos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"0","text":"## PROTOCOLO\\NADMINISTRACIÓN\\NANFOTERICINA B","guid":"","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"- Anfotericina B desoxicolato 50\\Nmg/día EV en lípidos 20%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"- Hidratación con suero\\Nfisiológico + electrolitos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"147","text":"- Monitorización de\\Nsignos vitales","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":150,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Hematología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Hematología","filename":"Paper. Neutropenia febril-2025","id":"map_1084","resolved_references":[]}